name: iShares 20+ Year U.S. Treasury Bond Index ETF (CAD-Hedged)
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide income by replicating, to the extent possible, the performance of an index that is broadly representative of U.S. Treasury bonds with remaining maturities greater than 20 years, net of expenses, and, to the extent possible, hedge any resulting U.S. dollar currency exposure back to Canadian dollars. The ETF seeks to provide income by replicating, to the extent possible, the performance of an index that is broadly representative of U.S. Treasury bonds with remaining maturities greater than 20 years, net of expenses, and, to the extent possible, hedge any resulting U.S. dollar currency exposure back to Canadian dollars. The current index for the ETF is the ICE U.S. Treasury 20+ Year Bond Index (CAD-Hedged).
